ProductRegistrationDelegate Protocol Reference

Conforms to NSObject
Declared in DIUserWithProduct.h

Overview

Use this delegate to receive callbacks for Product Registration.

– registerProductWithSuccess:

Called when product has been registered successfully.

- (void)registerProductWithSuccess:(NSDictionary *_Nullable)registrationResult

Parameters

registrationResult

Contains registraion informations for e.g. contractNumber, registrationDate, warrantyEndDate etc.

Discussion

Called when product has been registered successfully.
